\section{Requirements}
\subsection{Barcode Scanning Feature}
\begin{itemize}
    \item \textbf{Barcode Scanning via Camera}: Users can scan product barcodes using their smartphone camera.
    \item \textbf{QR Code Scanning Support}: Apply coupons or discounts via QR codes.
\end{itemize}

\subsection{Shopping Cart Feature}
\begin{itemize}
    \item Add, modify, or remove products.
    \item View total payment amount in real-time.
\end{itemize}

\subsection{Payment Features}
\begin{itemize}
    \item Choose and manage payment methods.
    \item Instant payment with a single click.
    \item View payment history and receipts.
\end{itemize}

\subsection{Promotions and Coupon Management}
\begin{itemize}
    \item Register and apply discount codes automatically.
    \item Reward programs applicable to purchases.
\end{itemize}

\subsection{Notifications}
\begin{itemize}
    \item Real-time notifications for promotions and payments.
\end{itemize}

\section{Development Environment}
\subsection{Software Platform}
A web application platform is suitable due to its accessibility, scalability, and cross-platform compatibility.

\subsection{Coding Languages}
JavaScript, TypeScript, HTML, and CSS frameworks will be used for development. Node.js and React Native are chosen for their extensive libraries.

\subsection{Cost Estimation}
\begin{tabular}{|l|l|p{8cm}|}
\hline
\textbf{Expense Attribute} & \textbf{Cost per Annum} & \textbf{Reasoning} \\
\hline
Web Hosting & \$1200-2400 & Platforms like AWS or Heroku. \\
Database Hosting & \$240-600 & For storing data securely online. \\
Outsourced API & \$600-1200 & For barcode scanning capabilities. \\
Domain Name & \$0-20 & To secure a domain name. \\
SSL & \$0-249 & For secure, encrypted connections. \\
\hline
\end{tabular}

\section{Specifications}
\subsection{Login Page}
Users enter a username and password for secure access.

\subsection{Register Page}
Usernames must be 2-20 characters long; passwords must be 8-15 characters with a mix of letters and numbers.

\subsection{User Information Page}
Manage user information, payment methods, and purchase history.

\subsection{Card Registration Page}
Register multiple cards for instant payment.

\subsection{Purchase History Page}
View and manage previous purchases.

\subsection{Barcode Scanning Page}
Users scan barcodes to retrieve item information and proceed with payment.

